p.k: A potential rival at Satis House gives Compeyson cause for concern. When a drunk prank goes dangerously wrong, Arthur realises the lengths to which Compeyson will go to achieve his aims. UK (2015). Cast: Stephen Rea, Tuppence Middleton, Mark Stanley, Robert Wilfort, Ben Starr, Tom Weston-Jones, Omid Djalili, Caroline Quentin, Pauline Collins, Wilson Radjou-Pujalte, Ned Dennehy, Adrian Rawlins, Jennifer Hennessy, Anton Lesser, Ellie Haddington, Alexandra Moen, Karl Johnson, Sophie Rundle, Peter Firth, John Heffernan, Richard Ridings, Bethany Muir, Imogen Faires, Christopher Fairbank, Richard Cordery. Director: Philippa Langdale.
